i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 398, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 547 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13560,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/13\/dua-enter-exit-mosque\/","url_meta":{"origin":13557,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for entering, leaving Masjid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Usayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you enters the mosque, let him say: O Allah, open for me the doors of your mercy. When he leaves, let him say: O Allah, I ask you for your favor.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15926,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/09\/05\/angels-bless-remain-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":13557,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Angels bless those who wait for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe prayer of a man in congregation is twenty-five times better than prayer in his home or shop. When he performs ablution in a good manner and leaves to the mosque only to perform the prayer,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Ri